10.71	Hatful_of_Hollow	Hatful of Hollow	Hatful of Hollow is a compilation album by the English rock band The Smiths, featuring BBC Radio 1 studio recordings and two contemporary singles with their B-sides. It was released on 12 November 1984 by the band's British record company, Rough Trade, just months after the band's debut, The Smiths. The album reached No. 7 on the UK album chart and stayed on the chart for 46 weeks. Eventually, on 9 November 1993, it was also released by their American label, Sire Records, which had initially declined to release the album.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/15/HatfulofHollow84.jpg/220px-HatfulofHollow84.jpg
